    "approaches": "# Approaches: 13.2 Coin change\n\n| Approach | File | Time | Space | When |\n|----------|------|------|-------|------|\n| Bottom Up Dp Min (primary) | `solution.go` | O(amount * len(coins)) | O(amount) | LeetCode 322 — minimum coins |\n| Top-down DP with memo (min coins) | `variants/top-down-dp.go` | O(amount * len(coins)) | O(amount) | Default; recursive flood fill (mutates grid) |\n\nDrill the **primary** blind first. Use variants when an interviewer asks for BFS vs DFS, recursive vs iterative, etc.",
